snippet.textDisplay:
Loving someone doesn't mean you need to be in relationship with them. Loving someone is adoring them from afar. I know you can't be mine but still a light of hope enlightens my heart. A little spark brings joy within me.
Love isn't bound by a promise or name
It blooms in silence, yet burns just the same. 
To cherish, to care, with nothing to claim.
A love that asks nothing yet always remains.
